---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import CTABand from "../components/CTABand.astro";
import { SITE } from "../data/site";
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="417 Web Co is one person: Peter Hartman, an engineer in Nixa, MO with 15 years of professional QA and infrastructure experience, born and raised in the 417."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="kicker">About</p>
      <h1>A one-man shop, not a marketing agency.</h1>
      <div class="grid grid-2 body">
        <div>
          <p class="lead">
            {SITE.name} is one person: {SITE.owner} — an engineer in {SITE.city},
            born and raised in the 417.
          </p>
          <p>
            Before opening this shop, I spent fifteen years making software work:
            seven of them solely responsible for quality on a high-traffic federal
            government website, on a fully remote engineering team — writing automated
            test suites that ran on every release, and authoring QA process
            documentation that helped the company earn CMMI Level&nbsp;3 certification.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today that same discipline goes into small-business websites: static-first
            builds that load instantly, automated tests before every update, structured
            data that helps Google understand your business, and infrastructure that's
            monitored and backed up — with restores actually tested, not assumed.
          </p>
          <p>
            It's my name on the work: every dollar you spend pays the person
            doing it, and it stays in the community. I take on a couple of
            builds a month, so every project gets my full attention.
          </p>
          <p>
            I respond fastest by email, and I'll always tell you the truth about
            what you need — including when the answer is "your current site is
            fine, don't pay anyone to rebuild it."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card signals">
          <h2 class="sr-only">Credentials at a glance</h2>
          <h3>Why hire me</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><b>15 years</b> professional engineering experience</li>
            <li><b>7 years</b> sole QA owner of a federal government website</li>
            <li><b>CMMI Level 3</b> process documentation author</li>
            <li><b>Every build tested</b> — automated suite runs before each update</li>
            <li><b>Born &amp; raised in the 417</b> — working from {SITE.city}, serving the whole area</li>
            <li><b>One-man shop</b> — the person you email is the person who builds</li>
            <li><b>Open source</b> — no license fees ever passed to you</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand />
</Base>

<style>
  .body { align-items: start; }
  .signals ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; color: var(--ink-soft); }
  .signals li { margin-bottom: 0.55rem; }
</style>
